import React from "react";
import Container from "./container"
const SignUp = () => {

  const form = <form>
    <labl>
      Name :
      <input />
    </labl>
  </form>
  return <>
    <Container closec="hidden" conclass="container" action={() => { }} content={form} />

}

export default SignUp;
